<abstract>
<t>This document describes a method for broadcasting IP data in a unidirectional manner using the vertical blanking interval of television signals.  It includes a description for compressing IP headers on unidirectional networks, a framing protocol identical to SLIP, a forward error correction scheme, and the NABTS byte structures.</t></abstract></front>

